The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm for feature extraction from high-dimensional data, specifically for image classification and regression tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SD (Sound). However, given the focus on supervised learning and image analysis, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
